          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 90-degree yield of the d(3He,gamma)5Li reaction",
                " has been measured from 2.3 to 11.2 MeV 3He energy.",
                "No clear evidence of a level in 5Li has been found",
                " over this energy range.",
                "The upper limits for the resonance integrated cross",
                " section  and  gamma-ray width were estimated to be",
                " about 15 micro-b*meV and 100 eV, respectively."
              ]
